Description: Aptura Shell desktop integration
 Installs Aptura Shell, session integration, and desktop defaults.
 The default desktop uses Aptura's own Wayland shell profile with labwc,
 waybar, wofi, Aptura branding, practical workstation tools, firmware
 visibility, and power controls. KDE Plasma remains available as a fallback
 session and application base.
